The paper discusses the testing of image classifiers using Deep Neural Networks (DNNs), which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the robustness of software systems, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The testing approach presented in the paper is based on class property violations, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG).
